  npc: 22
  sequence:
  - dialogueText: Three in a row. You're consistent, I'll give you that.
    buttonText: Last one
  - dialogueText: Technically, if you play again now, it'll be your third game of
      the day. Maybe the saying will finally be right.
    buttonText: I'm stuck anyway
  - dialogueText: That's the spirit. Let's see if your luck has any pulse left.
    buttonText: Cards
